        <UserObject label="&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;22&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;22&quot;&gt;ADO = Azure DevOps&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;24&quot; data-end=&quot;207&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Azure DevOps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; is a cloud-based DevOps platform from &lt;span class=&quot;&quot; data-state=&quot;closed&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;decorated-link&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; href=&quot;https://www.microsoft.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com&quot;&gt;Microsoft&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; that helps teams plan, develop, build, test, and deploy applications.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1shrdta&quot; data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;233&quot;&gt;Main Services in ADO&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11aa58c&quot; data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;238&quot; data-end=&quot;254&quot;&gt;Azure Boards&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;mbgpm7&quot; data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;270&quot;&gt;&#xa;Work Items&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;7emsik&quot; data-start=&quot;274&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot;&gt;&#xa;User Stories&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;178248m&quot; data-start=&quot;292&quot; data-end=&quot;299&quot;&gt;&#xa;Tasks&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1j42jor&quot; data-start=&quot;303&quot; data-end=&quot;309&quot;&gt;&#xa;Bugs&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18pe8rb&quot; data-start=&quot;313&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;Sprint Planning&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6wy0oi&quot; data-start=&quot;332&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;335&quot; data-end=&quot;350&quot;&gt;Azure Repos&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;354&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;5e8qgm&quot; data-start=&quot;354&quot; data-end=&quot;372&quot;&gt;&#xa;Git repositories&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;dunvss&quot; data-start=&quot;376&quot; data-end=&quot;387&quot;&gt;&#xa;Branching&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s11mun&quot; data-start=&quot;391&quot; data-end=&quot;406&quot;&gt;&#xa;Pull Requests&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;pyqmss&quot; data-start=&quot;410&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;&#xa;Code Reviews&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kfkzt3&quot; data-start=&quot;426&quot; data-end=&quot;523&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;429&quot; data-end=&quot;448&quot;&gt;Azure Pipelines&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;452&quot; data-end=&quot;523&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3q9t1x&quot; data-start=&quot;452&quot; data-end=&quot;470&quot;&gt;&#xa;CI/CD automation&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;qq2cnh&quot; data-start=&quot;474&quot; data-end=&quot;503&quot;&gt;&#xa;Build and Release pipelines&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;le0rog&quot; data-start=&quot;507&quot; data-end=&quot;523&quot;&gt;&#xa;YAML pipelines&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rd3tke&quot; data-start=&quot;525&quot; data-end=&quot;604&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;528&quot; data-end=&quot;548&quot;&gt;Azure Test Plans&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;552&quot; data-end=&quot;604&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1imilr8&quot; data-start=&quot;552&quot; data-end=&quot;568&quot;&gt;&#xa;Manual testing&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1b2mm1&quot; data-start=&quot;572&quot; data-end=&quot;584&quot;&gt;&#xa;Test cases&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;181a8to&quot; data-start=&quot;588&quot; data-end=&quot;604&quot;&gt;&#xa;Test execution&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;elnv0l&quot; data-start=&quot;606&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;609&quot; data-end=&quot;628&quot;&gt;Azure Artifacts&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;632&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;19a5uf5&quot; data-start=&quot;632&quot; data-end=&quot;652&quot;&gt;&#xa;Package management&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1trde0e&quot; data-start=&quot;656&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;&#xa;NuGet, npm, Maven packages&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;qwvex5&quot; data-start=&quot;686&quot; data-end=&quot;721&quot;&gt;Interview Answer (Spoken Style)&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;blockquote data-start=&quot;723&quot; data-end=&quot;1074&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;725&quot; data-end=&quot;1074&quot;&gt;&quot;Azure DevOps is Microsoft&#39;s DevOps platform used for end-to-end software delivery. We use Azure Repos for source code management, Azure Boards for project tracking, and Azure Pipelines for CI/CD automation. In my current project, I use YAML-based pipelines to provision Azure infrastructure through Terraform and deploy applications automatically.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" link="&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;22&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;22&quot;&gt;ADO = Azure DevOps&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;24&quot; data-end=&quot;207&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Azure DevOps&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; is a cloud-based DevOps platform from &lt;span class=&quot;&quot; data-state=&quot;closed&quot;&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;decorated-link&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot; href=&quot;https://www.microsoft.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com&quot;&gt;Microsoft&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; that helps teams plan, develop, build, test, and deploy applications.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1shrdta&quot; data-start=&quot;209&quot; data-end=&quot;233&quot;&gt;Main Services in ADO&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;684&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11aa58c&quot; data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;238&quot; data-end=&quot;254&quot;&gt;Azure Boards&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;mbgpm7&quot; data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;270&quot;&gt;&#xa;Work Items&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;7emsik&quot; data-start=&quot;274&quot; data-end=&quot;288&quot;&gt;&#xa;User Stories&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;178248m&quot; data-start=&quot;292&quot; data-end=&quot;299&quot;&gt;&#xa;Tasks&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1j42jor&quot; data-start=&quot;303&quot; data-end=&quot;309&quot;&gt;&#xa;Bugs&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18pe8rb&quot; data-start=&quot;313&quot; data-end=&quot;330&quot;&gt;&#xa;Sprint Planning&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;6wy0oi&quot; data-start=&quot;332&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;335&quot; data-end=&quot;350&quot;&gt;Azure Repos&lt;/strong&gt;&#xa;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;354&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;5e8qgm&quot; data-start=&quot;354&quot; data-end=&quot;372&quot;&gt;&#xa;Git repositories&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;dunvss&quot; data-start=&quot;376&quot; data